            <title>[THRIFT-1825] Debian Packaging: cpp libs no longer included since 0.8</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1825</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From Thrift 0.8, cpp libs are no longer included in libthrift0 package.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m attaching a very small patch that solves the issue; though I&apos;m not an expert of debian packaging and I worked it out through a little hacking, it should work.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
